1:21:28.805 --> 1:21:31.141
- It was more about him.
- I honestly-- I really don't care.

1:21:32.059 --> 1:21:33.268
You hungry?

1:21:33.894 --> 1:21:36.313
Yeah. I could eat.
Let me just put my stuff down.

1:21:41.235 --> 1:21:43.403
<i>Did you have any luck finding that girl?</i>

1:21:43.403 --> 1:21:47.157
Not yet. Braddock had a lead
down in Miami but it was a bust.

1:21:48.909 --> 1:21:49.785
Honey, you know,

1:21:49.785 --> 1:21:55.165
