and confusing and unfair.

1:21:55.165 --> 1:22:00.003
But I don't think that finding her
is gonna make you feel any better.

1:22:01.421 --> 1:22:02.422
I disagree.

1:22:03.298 --> 1:22:04.424
Yeah, well--

1:22:05.008 --> 1:22:07.928
Okay. Hang on, I-- I have
something I wanna show you.

1:22:07.928 --> 1:22:09.054
So, I...

1:22:10.806 --> 1:22:14.226
started looking for apartments for you.

1:22:14.226 --> 1:22:16.395
These are all downtown near the bookstore,

1:22:16.395 --> 1:22:18.564
so it wouldn't be much of a commute.

1:22:18.564 --> 1:22:20.107
- What is this?
- Well, I told you.

1:22:20.107 --> 1:22:22.693
I'm gonna have to sell this apartment,
so I want you to find a place.

1:22:22.693 --> 1:22:24.528
