1:24:48.589 --> 1:24:50.465
- Can I go in and talk to her?
- I'm gonna go with you.

1:24:50.465 --> 1:24:52.134
No. I'm okay.

1:25:03.437 --> 1:25:05.063
Did she say anything else?

1:25:06.773 --> 1:25:07.941
You have any more insight?

1:25:09.943 --> 1:25:11.320
