1:25:23.624 --> 1:25:24.708
You all right, sweetheart?

1:25:24.708 --> 1:25:25.792
Yeah.

1:25:28.754 --> 1:25:30.088
Yeah. I'm okay.

1:25:30.797 --> 1:25:33.383
It's weird.
