1:26:40.492 --> 1:26:43.245
Okay. If she's gonna stay here,
then I need to talk to her.

1:26:43.787 --> 1:26:45.831
- No, wait. She needs to rest.
- No, I should.

1:27:32.503 --> 1:27:33.504
Sandra?

1:27:35.464 --> 1:27:36.465
Sandra?

1:27:41.970 --> 1:27:43.138
Hi, I'm Madeline.

1:27:44.139 --> 1:27:47.601
I was married to Tom's father.
I'm his stepmother.

1:27:50.187 --> 1:27:53.565
Suck my dick, you lying bitch.

1:27:55.609 --> 1:27:57.653
Yeah, I know who you are, Madeline.

1:27:59.613 --> 1:28:01.240
Max told me the whole score.

1:28:02.991 --> 1:28:06.203
That you set the cops on him,
but then had to beg him to come back.

1:28:06.703 --> 1:28:10.958
How there was an old man who was dying
and was gonna leave behind a fortune,

1:28:10.958 --> 1:28:12.501
and all we needed to do was...

1:28:13.919 --> 1:28:15.087
nudge aside the son

1:28:15.087 --> 1:28:17.881
so that his very full of shit widow
