1:28:20.801 --> 1:28:23.387
I wanna confess. Confess to it all

1:28:24.054 --> 1:28:26.014
and get this off my chest.

1:28:26.014 --> 1:28:27.933
Do me a favor and get Tom. Tom?

1:28:27.933 --> 1:28:29.101
