1:28:53.792 --> 1:28:55.169
Then what can I do for you?

1:29:00.674 --> 1:29:01.884
I want Max.

1:29:03.510 --> 1:29:05.095
I wanna see Max.

1:29:07.097 --> 1:29:10.434
I wanna look into his face,
and I want him to see what he did to me.

1:29:12.811 --> 1:29:14.062
I wanna see Max.

1:29:15.522 --> 1:29:17.941
Honey, I don't know where he is.

1:29:17.941 --> 1:29:19.318
Well, you better find out.

1:29:20.611 --> 1:29:23.906
Or I will tell everyone in the next room
who you really fucking are.

1:29:32.831 --> 1:29:33.916
She can stay.

